## Weight Tuning

The scoring weights are constants in getTopItems.js. Adjust if the ranking feels wrong:

    Current: { days3: 5, days7: 3, days30: 1, presence: 4 }

    - Increase days3 to make very recent items dominate more.
    - Increase presence to reward items that span multiple windows.
    - Decrease days30 if old items are ranking too high.

The presence bonus (max 12 for an item in all 3 windows) is roughly equivalent to
logging an item twice in the 3-day window (score 10). This feels right — an item used
consistently over time should compete with something used twice yesterday.
